Package common

Class ExtensionRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.ExtensionRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class ExtensionRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The ExtensionRequest class represents a request for an extension made by an applicant for a specific test. The request includes information about the applicant, the test ID, the details of the extension request, and the current status of the request.
    See Also:
